714836f.text:
East 93rd Street, west from but not including Madison to Fifth Aves. Note Central Park forming the west side of the latter Ave.
June 22, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.

714837f-a.text:
East 93rd Street, south side, west from (No. 16, extreme left) but not including Madison to Fifth Aves. (right), showing a row of 4-story basement houses, Nos. 16 to 6 included. At the S.E. corner of Fifth Ave.
is a new apartment house No. 1116.
June 22, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
